{
  "id": "63873dd63cb81a0021db246d",
  "title": "石が流れて木の葉が沈む",
  "created": 1669807576,
  "updated": 1674951253,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63873dd63cb81a0021db246d",
      "text": "石が流れて木の葉が沈む",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807576,
      "updated": 1669807576
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd8e600350000c322e3",
      "text": ">本来は軽い[木の葉]が流れ、重い[石]は沈むものなのに、それが逆になっていることから、物事が通常の[道理]とは逆になっていることのたとえ。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807576,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322e4",
      "text": "> 世の中が[理不尽]であることを嘆く言葉。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322e5",
      "text": "> 『[新語]』に「夫れ衆口の毀誉は、石を浮かべて木を沈ます（多くの人が言う[悪口]や[褒め言葉]は、[真理]とは反対である）」とある。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1674911558
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322e6",
      "text": "[https://kotowaza-dictionary.jp/k0635/ 石が流れて木の葉が沈む - 故事ことわざ辞典]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322e7",
      "text": "　>『新語』（しんご）は、古代中国の[前漢]初期（紀元前200年頃）に[陸賈]が著した書籍である。[漢]の[高祖]（[劉邦]）の求めに応じて書かれ、諸国の興亡の原因を説く。全12篇が今に伝わるが、真に陸賈が著したものかどうか疑う[新語偽作説]がある。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322e8",
      "text": "　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/新語 新語 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322e9",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/陸賈 陸賈 - Wikipedia]（りくか）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63d5ba54e60035000043a763",
      "text": "「流れる石」として例えば[軽石]がある[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1674951252,
      "updated": 1674951253
    },
    {
      "id": "63d5ba56e60035000043a765",
      "text": "　[多孔質]なので水に浮く（ただし時間と共に水が染み込んで沈む）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1674951253,
      "updated": 1674951253
    },
    {
      "id": "63d5ba56e60035000043a766",
      "text": "　2021年に[福徳岡ノ場]の[噴火]に伴って噴出した軽石が、各地に漂着して騒動となったことは記憶に新しい",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1674951253,
      "updated": 1674951253
    },
    {
      "id": "63d5ba56e60035000043a767",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/福徳岡ノ場 福徳岡ノ場 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1674951253,
      "updated": 1674951253
    },
    {
      "id": "63d5ba55e60035000043a764",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1674951252,
      "updated": 1674951252
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322eb",
      "text": "類似表現",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322ec",
      "text": "　[浮石沈木]（ふせきちんぼく）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322ed",
      "text": "　 >一般大衆の無責任な言論が、道理に反して威力をもつたとえ。水に沈むはずの石を浮かせ、水に浮くはずの木を沈める意から。▽「石いしを浮うかせ木きを沈しずむ」と訓読する。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322ee",
      "text": "　 >出典『[魏志]』[孫礼伝]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322ef",
      "text": "　 [https://dictionary.goo.ne.jp/word/浮石沈木/ 浮石沈木(ふせきちんぼく)の意味・使い方 - 四字熟語一覧 - goo辞書]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63d53dc8e5172d0000b15b84",
      "text": "　[石に漱ぎ流れに枕す]を連想した[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1674919373,
      "updated": 1674919409
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f1",
      "text": "「石が流れて木の葉が沈む」は[必殺仕業人](ひっさつしわざにん)のオープニング[ナレーション]にも出てくる[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f2",
      "text": "　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/必殺仕業人 必殺仕業人 - Wikipedia]（1976年放送）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f4",
      "text": ">必殺口上",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f5",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f6",
      "text": "> あんた　この世をどう思う",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f7",
      "text": "> どうってことねえか",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f8",
      "text": "> あんた　それでも生きてんの",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322f9",
      "text": "> この世の川を見てごらんな",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322fa",
      "text": "> [石が流れて木の葉が沈む]　いけねえなあ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322fb",
      "text": "> 面白いかい",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322fc",
      "text": "> あんた　死んだふりはよそうぜ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322fd",
      "text": "> やっぱり木の葉はぴらぴら流れて欲しいんだよ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322fe",
      "text": "> 石ころはじょぼんと沈んでもらいてぇんだよ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c322ff",
      "text": "> おいあんた　聞いてんの",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c32300",
      "text": "> 聞いてんのかよ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c32301",
      "text": "> あらぁ　もう死んでやがらぁ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c32302",
      "text": "> はぁ…　菜っ葉ばかり食ってやがったからなぁ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c32303",
      "text": "> （語り：[宇崎竜童]）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c32304",
      "text": "[https://dic.pixiv.net/a/必殺仕業人 必殺仕業人 (ひっさつしわざにん)とは【ピクシブ百科事典】]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1669807577,
      "updated": 1669807577
    },
    {
      "id": "63873dd9e600350000c32305",
